item.title: Frankie Vaughan - Stella By Starlight
item.description:
작곡: Sung by
KY: 8931

The song
a robin sings
Through years
of endless springs
The murmur
of a brook
At evening tides
that ripples
Through a nook
where two lovers hide
That great
symphonic theme
That’s stella
by starlight
And not a dream
my heart and I agree
She’s everything
on this earth to me-
